Mystery Fantasy - Volume 1 is the first collection of 26 music tracks dedicated to a mysterious and dark atmosphere. It can also be used for horror or Halloween. These tracks are ideal for your games related to the mystery world, horror world, callings and many other categories.

This package is produced by Carlo Luzi a composer with several years of experience in music production.

The package includes several multiple loops, and several editable versions for all your editing needs.
